      • timerComment

        public java.lang.String timerComment​(fr.cnrs.iees.graph.impl.TreeGraphDataNode function,
                                     TwFunctionTypes ftype)
        This method works out the comment to add to generated files regarding Timer information. Since each method in the generated model class file can follow a different Timer, a specific comment is generated for every method.
        Parameters:
        function - the specification node of a TwFunction descendant
        ftype - the function type of the the function
        Returns:
        the comment as a string ready for insertion in source code
